00:00:06.110 --> 00:00:09.200
Our guest is Jan Jarboe Russell.

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:11.120
She is a journalist.

00:00:11.120 --> 00:00:15.880
Her newest book is "The
Train to Crystal City."

00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:19.380
Jan Jarboe Russell is a Nieman
Fellow, a contributing editor

00:00:19.380 --> 00:00:21.340
for the "Texas Monthly."

00:00:21.340 --> 00:00:22.900
She has written for
the "San Antonio

00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:25.280
Express News," "The New
York Times," "Slate,"

00:00:25.280 --> 00:00:26.940
and other magazines.

00:00:26.940 --> 00:00:31.530
Jan is the author also of
"Lady Bird, a Biography of Mrs.

00:00:31.530 --> 00:00:35.260
Johnson" and has also
compiled and edited

00:00:35.260 --> 00:00:37.380
"They Lived to Tell the Tale."

00:00:37.380 --> 00:00:40.870
